  "paragraphs": [
    "Keep Your Car Looking New—No Matter What Colorado Throws At It",
    "Front Range Detail Studio, conveniently located in South Denver, has been Colorado’s leading provider of immaculate auto, watercraft, Motorcoach, and RV detailing services. Combining expert craftsmanship with unrivaled customer service, we excel in vehicle wraps, clear bra, PPF, ceramic coating, window tinting, polishing, paint correction and gel coat restoration. Whether you desire increased durability, superior aesthetics, or ultimate protection for your cherished possessions, trust our skilled team to transform them beyond expectations and create a lasting statement of beauty. Rest assured that your prized asset will receive the pampering it deserves, ensuring a show-stopping shine that commands attention for the long road ahead",
    "Perfect for regular upkeep and protection.",
    "✔ Duration: ~2 hours✔ Recommended Frequency: Every 1-2 months",
    "Restore and protect your car’s paint for a flawless finish.",
    "✔ Duration: ~4-5 hours✔ Recommended Frequency: Every 3-6 months",
    "Deep clean your car’s interior for a fresh, like-new feel.",
    "✔ Duration: ~3-4 hours✔ Recommended Frequency: Every 4-6 months",
    "Our most comprehensive package — for vehicles that need full restoration.",
    "✔ Duration: ~6-8 hours✔ Recommended Frequency: Twice a year",
    "1-Year Protection",
    "3-Year Protection",
    "6-Year Protection",
    "9-Year & Lifetime Protection",
    "Over 15 years experience in the automotive detailing industry. Car, Trucks, Semi Trucks, SUVs, RVs, Boats & Watercraft.",
    "Our clients have one thing in common: they love their vehicle. From the Class A motorhome to the two-door convertible, our team of detail specialists are equipped and experienced to handle all detailing needs anywhere in Metro Denver.",
    "12559 E Broncos Pkwy, Centennial, CO 80112",
    "Front Range Detail Studio",
    "Crafting Radiance. Preserving Elegance. Colorado's One Stop Shop for All Your Vehicle Care Needs"
  ],
